WEBVTT

00:02:28.280 --> 00:02:30.176
nothing better than these neck pillows.

00:02:30.200 --> 00:02:33.256
They're designed
to make you more comfortable --

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:35.096
(Laughter)

00:02:35.120 --> 00:02:36.336
except they don't.

00:02:36.360 --> 00:02:39.320
(Laughter)

00:02:40.200 --> 00:02:41.640
So I never sleep on airplanes.

00:02:42.880 --> 00:02:46.976
What I do occasionally
is I fall into a sort of painful coma.

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:50.496
And when I wake up from that,

00:02:50.520 --> 00:02:53.176
I have the most terrible
taste in my mouth.

00:02:53.200 --> 00:02:56.536
It's a taste that's so bad,
it cannot be described with words,

00:02:56.560 --> 00:02:57.936
but it can be drawn.

00:02:57.960 --> 00:03:03.896
(Laughter)